                title = "Community GOTY 2022 Winners",
                link = "https://www.giantbomb.com/articles/community-goty-2022-winners/1100-6280/",
                description = "<![CDATA[ <figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/1992/3435176-godofwarragnaro%CC%88k_20221111143941.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3435176\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 3840px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/1992/3435176-godofwarragnaro%CC%88k_20221111143941.jpg\"><img alt=\"No Caption Provided\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/1992/3435176-godofwarragnaro%CC%88k_20221111143941.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/1992/3435176-godofwarragnaro%CC%88k_20221111143941.jpg 3840w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/1992/3435176-godofwarragnaro%CC%88k_20221111143941.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/1992/3435176-godofwarragnaro%CC%88k_20221111143941.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" data-width=\"960\"></a></figure><p>Hey everyone! These are the results of the community GOTY - the results of which (resultingly) have been resulted below. This year, 712 of you submitted a top ten list, for a total of 5854 votes (not everyone always puts in ten games, which is fine!) on 500 different games. Wow! Amazing!</p><p>It's another year with a blowout winner, as <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/elden-ring/3030-73745/\">Elden Ring</a> wins going away, with almost triple the weighted points of the #2 game, <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/vampire-survivors/3030-84714/\">Vampire Survivors</a>. <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/tunic/3030-55097/\">Tunic</a>, <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/god-of-war-ragnarok/3030-80643/\">GOW: Ragnarok</a>, and everyone's favorite sleeper hiut, <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/horizon-forbidden-west/3030-78969/\">Horizon: Forbidden West</a>, also round out the top ten. I don't think it was necessarily an <em>amazing</em> year for games as we're still seeing the ramifications of COVID on development, but I still had fun with a few of these games!</p><p>I apologize for the delay in publishing this! It honestly slipped my mind as January obviously had a lot of stuff going on there with a variety of emergencies and still adapting to the new company. My bad!</p><p>As per usual, we don't always separate out expansions or new ports or games leaving early access in our wiki so if you see stuff like <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/the-stanley-parable-ultra-deluxe/3030-86034/\">The Stanley Parable: Ultra Deluxe</a> you can assume that it's referring to a recent release.</p><p><strong>Weighted Votes </strong>(1st place counts more than 2nd, and so on)</p><table data-max-width=\"true\"><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"> </th><th scope=\"col\">Game</th><th scope=\"col\">Number of Votes</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1.</td><td><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/elden-ring/3030-73745/\">Elden Ring</a></td><td>393</td></tr><tr><td>2.</td><td><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/vampire-survivors/3030-84714/\">Vampire Survivors</a></td><td>140</td></tr><tr><td>3.</td><td><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/god-of-war-ragnarok/3030-80643/\">God of War Ragnarök</a></td><td>107</td></tr><tr><td>4.</td><td><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/tunic/3030-55097/\">Tunic</a></td><td>95</td></tr><tr><td>5.</td><td><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/pentiment/3030-86451/\">Pentiment</a></td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>6.</td><td><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/horizon-forbidden-west/3030-78969/\">Horizon Forbidden West</a></td><td>53</td></tr><tr><td>7.</td><td><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/neon-white/3030-81830/\">Neon White</a></td><td>53</td></tr><tr><td>8.</td><td><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/citizen-sleeper/3030-83035/\">Citizen Sleeper</a></td><td>44</td></tr><tr><td>9.</td><td><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/xenoblade-chronicles-3/3030-85427/\">Xenoblade Chronicles 3</a></td><td>42</td></tr><tr><td>10.</td><td><a href