                        "<![CDATA[ i></ul> <p>The Xbox Series X launched globally on November 10, 2020, giving Microsoft a two-day head start against Sony&apos;s PS5, which was released on November 12 (in select countries and November 19 for the rest of the world). Check out our <a href=\"https://www.techradar.com/reviews/ps5\">PS5 rev ]]>\n" +
