                        "<![CDATA[ ead our full <a href=\"https://www.techradar.com/reviews/xbox-series-s\">Xbox Series S review</a>.</p><p>While this isn’t exactly pocket money, it’s a decent price for the new Xbox. It’s the same price as the (now discontinued) <a href=\"https://www.techradar.com/reviews/original-2013-xbox-one\">X ]]>\n" +
