                    "<![CDATA[ olithic even. Despite its weight and fairly large size, it looks considerably smaller than its measurements would suggest. We found it slotted with ease into an Ikea Kallax shelving unit (39cm x 39cm), when oriented either horizontally or vertically, and comfortably blended in with its surroundings. ]]>\n" +
                    "<![CDATA[  </p><p>The Xbox Series X design is something you’ll either love or hate – we found it a welcome change from the previous low-profile Xbox consoles. It&apos;s sleek, modern, and looks like something a grown-up would actually want to own, and it&apos;s a nice evolution from the flat-but-compact ]]>\n" +
